# Dastro 2.0 — manual patch

Dastro 2.0 upgrades to Astro 6.

## 1. Update local dependencies

```sh
npm update --save
```

## 2. Bump `schema-dts` to v2

If still on v1, install the latest:

```sh
npm i -S schema-dts@^2.0.0
```

## 3. Move `fonts` out of `experimental` in `astro.config.ts`

Astro 6 promotes fonts to stable. Un-nest the `fonts` array:

```diff
-  experimental: {
-    fonts: [
-      { /* ... */ },
-    ],
-  },
+  fonts: [
+    { /* ... */ },
+  ],
```

## 4. Astro 6 migration

Follow the official upgrade guide for any other changes required in your own project code: https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/upgrade-to/v6/
